  "description": "# Rotterdam-The Hague · RTM\n\nThe Rotterdam-The Hague metro corridor in the Netherlands' Randstad region; the port city and the seat of government, connected by rail. Coverage spans both cities and the dense urban belt between them.\n\n## Coverage\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Region</strong></td><td>Rotterdam-The Hague metro, South Holland (NL)</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding Box</strong></td><td>3.947, 51.805 → 4.641, 52.137</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>~1,745 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Population Summary\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Metro Population</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,500,000</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">712,179</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Map Statistics\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Buildings Indexed</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,146,671</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">415</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Population Nodes</strong></td><td align=\"right\">10,723</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Median Commute Distance</strong></td><td align=\"right\">11.3 km</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Mean Commute Distance</strong></td><td align=\"right\">12.4 km</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Additional Features\n\n- **Building Collision** — A buildings index of 1,146,671 structures is included, providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings (multi-level depth data included).\n- **Road & Runway Overlays** — Road network plus runway/taxiway geometry are bundled, covering Rotterdam The Hague Airport and surface routing across the corridor.",
